mpk

This is an command-line tool to calculate project schedules. Define tasks, dependencies, and a start date, and mpk will calculate the start and end dates for each task.

Features:
- Define non-work days of the week (such as Sunday or Monday)
- Tasks may have any number of predecessors
- Milestones can be added as tasks without durations
- Tasks may have sub-tasks
- Output is a schedule, listing each task and its calculated start and end dates
- Diagnosis output is available, showing detailed data for each task

